@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Terms of sale · White Stitches";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "The agreement between you and White Stitches when you buy from us.";
}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero__inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">@L["Legal · Terms"]</span>
    <h1 class="page-hero__title">@L["Terms of sale."]</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__lede">@L["The agreement between you and White Stitches when you buy from us."]</p>
    <p class="page-hero__meta">Last updated · 1 May 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="policy">
  <div class="policy__inner">
    <aside class="policy__toc" aria-label="@L["On this page"]">
      <span class="eyebrow">@L["On this page"]</span>
      <ol class="policy__toc-list">
    <li><a href="#agreement">@L["Your agreement with us"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#orders">@L["Placing an order"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#pricing">@L["Pricing & payment"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#delivery">@L["Delivery & risk"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#returns">@L["Returns & refunds"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#warranty">@L["Quality & defects"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#intellectual">@L["Intellectual property"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#liability">@L["Limits on liability"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#disputes">@L["Disputes & governing law"]</a></li>
      </ol>
    </aside>

    <main class="policy__main">
      <section class="policy-section" id="agreement">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Your agreement with us"]</h2>
        <p>By placing an order on whitestiches.kw, you agree to these Terms of Sale. The contract is between you and <strong>White Stitches Trading Company W.L.L.</strong>, registered in Kuwait under CR 12345/2024.</p>
         <p>You must be at least 18 years old to place an order. By checking out, you confirm you are.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="orders">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Placing an order"]</h2>
        <p>When you click <strong>Place Order</strong>, you make a binding offer to buy the items in your cart at the displayed price. We accept that offer when we send you the order confirmation email.</p>
         <p>Occasionally, we may decline an order — typically because of stock errors, payment issues, or suspected fraud. In that case, we&rsquo;ll refund any payment immediately and explain why.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="pricing">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Pricing & payment"]</h2>
        <p>All prices are in <strong>Kuwaiti Dinar (KWD)</strong> and include 5% VAT where applicable. Prices for orders shipped to other GCC countries display VAT for that country at checkout.</p>
         <p>Payment is taken at the time of order placement (or, for buy-now-pay-later, according to the schedule set by Tabby or Tamara).</p>
         <p>If a price is listed incorrectly due to a typo or system error, we reserve the right to cancel the order and issue a full refund — even if we&rsquo;ve already confirmed it.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="delivery">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Delivery & risk"]</h2>
        <p>Risk of loss passes to you once the courier hands over the package. We insure all shipments and will resolve loss or damage in transit.</p>
         <p>Delivery times are estimates, not guarantees. See <a href="/shipping" class="link-inline">Shipping &amp; Delivery</a> for details.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="returns">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Returns & refunds"]</h2>
        <p>Your full returns rights are set out in our <a href="/returns-policy" class="link-inline">Returns Policy</a>. Briefly: 14 days, unworn, original tags, refunds to original payment method.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="warranty">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Quality & defects"]</h2>
        <p>Every piece is inspected before dispatch. If you receive something defective, faulty, or not as described, contact us within 14 days and we&rsquo;ll replace it or refund you in full — including return shipping.</p>
         <p>This is in addition to your statutory consumer rights under Kuwaiti law.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="intellectual">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Intellectual property"]</h2>
        <p>All content on whitestiches.kw — logos, product photography, copy, designs — is the property of White Stitches Trading Company W.L.L. and protected by copyright.</p>
         <p>You may not use, copy or distribute our content without written permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="liability">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Limits on liability"]</h2>
        <p>We accept liability for losses you suffer as a direct result of our breach of these terms, up to the value of the affected order.</p>
         <p>We are not liable for indirect losses (loss of profit, business, opportunity), unless caused by our gross negligence or wilful misconduct.</p>
         <p>Nothing in these terms limits your statutory rights as a consumer.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="disputes">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Disputes & governing law"]</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Kuwait. Any dispute we cannot resolve directly will be settled in the Kuwaiti courts.</p>
         <p>We&rsquo;d much rather resolve things over WhatsApp than in court — please reach out before escalating anywhere else.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</section>

